t is being renovated, hotels or guesthouses are very limited here. The only places you could stay are <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/balat-akin\/\" target=\"_blank\">Akin<\/a>, <a aria-label=\" (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/balat-house\/\" target=\"_blank\">Balat House<\/a>, <a aria-label=\"Educa Suites (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/balat-educa\/\" target=\"_blank\">Educa Suites<\/a>, and <a aria-label=\"Hotel Troya (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/balat-troya\/\" target=\"_blank\">Hotel Troya<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/booking\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Discover great stays in the Balat area<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to visit Balat, Istanbul<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Balat is best to reach by bus or ferry. The ferry point named Fener is direct across the main street of Balat. At that same location is a <a aria-label=\"bus stop (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/ARqgvBmdezHYd86t9\" target=\"_blank\">bus stop<\/a> where many buses stop. Use Google Maps to plan your trip.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Tip: <\/strong>Save on expenses in Istanbul with the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/istanbul-welcome-card-premium\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Welcome Card<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry.jpg\" alt=\"istanbul transportation ferry\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"istanbul transportation ferry\" class=\"wp-image-14834 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\/23134624\/istanbul-transportation-ferry-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/06\